title: Episode 146 w/ Talib Kweli and Dead Prez

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Dead Prez and returning guest Talib Kweli. They talk about the state of hip hop, hip hop media, Kanye, health, conciousness, and a lot more.
